<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32.1 (July 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Final Flight (R)</b></li><ul><li>Damage fall off on this ability per target hit has been increased to 10%, up from 8%.</li><li>The minimum damage for subsequent targets hit after the first has been reduced to 50%, down from 60%.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32 (July 9th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Branching Blade (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The secondary hit damage on this ability has been reduced to 100% of the primary damage, down from 120%.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 30 (May 27th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Branching Blade (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been increased to 10/9/8/7/6 seconds, up from 9/8/7/6/5.</li></ul><li><B>Final Flight (R)</B></li><ul><li>The power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.65, down from 0.7.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Branching Blade (Q)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 11%.</li></ul><li>The Chase (W)</li><ul><li>The movement speed duration gained when activating this ability has been increased to 3 seconds, up from 2.</li></ul><li>Wing Clip (E)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 675, from previous value of 750.</li></ul><li>Final Flight (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 1900, from previous value of 2100.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 17 (November 7, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Branching Blade (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been changed to 60/95/130/165/200, from 55/95/135/175/215.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 11 (August 29, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug with Nissa's passive that caused her pet, Tal'ah, to get stuck in the first brush she entered.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Base Movement Speed reduced to 370, down from 385.</li><li><B>Final Flight (R)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 125/225/325 per hit, down from 150/250/350.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 5 (July 18, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Branching Blade (Q)</B></li><ul><li> The base damage on this ability has been reduced to 55/95/135/175/215, down from 70/110/150/190/230.</li></ul><li><B>Final Flight (R)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage on this ability has been reduced to 150/250/350 per hit, down from 175/275/375 per hit.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Branching Blade (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The secondary projectile procced by this ability has had its range reduced to 500, down from 530.</li></ul><li><B>The Chase (W)</B></li><ul><li>The passive haste bonus granted by this ability has been decreased to 15/20/25/30/35, down from 16/22/28/34/40.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 1 (June 06, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Final Flight (R)</B><ul><li>Fixed a bug where Final Flight would sometimes trigger 3 damage events instead of 2 if it hit a target at maximum range.</li></ul></li></ul>